  "text": "The SPM samples are listed in Table 1 and sampling positions are shown in Fig. 2 . Six SPM samples were collected close to the water surface and thebottom of the Rhône River at three different stations (RW1, RW2 and RW3). At the river mouth (RW4), the samples were collected at four different water depths. The hydrodynamics and mixing of river water with marine water in the estuary is typical of a micro-tidal salt wedge estuary [CITATION_1] .",
